---
title: Mexican Chicken Wraps with Apple-Beet Slaw and Potato Wedges
description: Well, hello Mr. Beet! You’re looking awfully delicious! We’re making the best of wonderful seasonal vegetables in our Mexican chicken wraps with a yummy apple- beet slaw and potato wedges.
